WEBVTT

00:03:29.394 --> 00:03:32.386
Sometimes that's 40 minutes,
usually it's less than five.

00:03:33.173 --> 00:03:35.172
She loves this flexibility.

00:03:35.196 --> 00:03:37.596
It's how she saw doctors in Somalia.

00:03:38.236 --> 00:03:41.323
And I love it, because I don't pay
staff to do scheduling,

00:03:41.347 --> 00:03:44.644
and we have a zero no-show rate
and a zero late-show rate.

00:03:44.668 --> 00:03:47.713
(Laughter)

00:03:47.737 --> 00:03:52.303
(Applause)

00:03:52.327 --> 00:03:54.009
It makes business sense.

00:03:54.970 --> 00:03:57.319
Another difference is our office layout.

00:03:57.343 --> 00:03:59.899
Our exam rooms open
right to the waiting room,

00:03:59.923 --> 00:04:02.391
our medical providers
room their own patients,